@startuml Skills Architecture
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

title Skills Architecture and Activation Flow

rectangle "Skills Repository\n(~/.copilot/skills/)" as Repo #LightBlue

rectangle "architect" as Architect #LightGreen
rectangle "dev-workflow" as DevWorkflow #LightGreen
rectangle "mcp-builder" as McpBuilder #LightGreen
rectangle "pdf" as Pdf #LightGreen
rectangle "recursive-context" as RecursiveContext #LightGreen
rectangle "sys-env" as SysEnv #LightGreen
rectangle "web-scraper" as WebScraper #LightGreen

rectangle "OpenCode Platform\n(~/.config/opencode/skills/)" as OpenCode #LightYellow

rectangle "Conversation Start" as Conversation #LightCoral

Repo --> Architect : contains
Repo --> DevWorkflow : contains
Repo --> McpBuilder : contains
Repo --> Pdf : contains
Repo --> RecursiveContext : contains
Repo --> SysEnv : contains
Repo --> WebScraper : contains

Architect --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh
DevWorkflow --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh
McpBuilder --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh
Pdf --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh
RecursiveContext --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh
SysEnv --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh
WebScraper --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh

OpenCode --> Conversation : activate_all.py\n(validates & loads)

note right of OpenCode
  Automatic activation
  at conversation start.
  AI uses skills autonomously.
end note

note over Repo
  Central hub for all skills.
  Managed with Git & CI/CD.
end note

@enduml